<h1>DASH Store Miami</h1>
<p>South Beach Miami where DASH Miami is located, is a very popular spot among tourists and Miami locals alike.  The nightlife on the blocks surrounding 815 Washington Ave are full of clubs, discos, cafe' crowds dining outdoors, music, and lots of people.  This DASH store stocks many stylish fashions that are fit for the local culture.  Platform Kim Kardashian Shoes, Short Skirts, and of course the accessories to match.  Handbags, boutique jewelry, womens belts, and several other must-have accessories when visiting South Beach.  DASH Miami of course, has swimwear including hot bikinis that are so common on South Beach.  Sunglasses and other beach gear are part of the store product line.  DASH Miami has a pretty extensive line of fashion accessories in comparison to that of its womens apparel selections.</p>
<h1>DASH Miami Staff</h1>
<p>The DASH Miami staff is handpicked by Kourtney and Kloe Kardashian.  They conied the title "<em>DASH Dolls</em>" for the DASH Miami staff.  The Kardashians try to select local girls who are passionate about and know South Beach Fashion.  If DASH Miami has a larger clothing selection, it would probably be the most popular DASH boutique.  For the time being <a href="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/dash-stores/dash-clothing-la/">DASH clothing LA</a> is still the highest rated of the D-A-S-H Boutiques among DASH patrons.  If you have something to comment about DASH Miami, please do.</p>  
<p>See Ratings & Reviews on <a href="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/dash-store-reviews-clothing/dash-miami-fl-ratings-reviews/">DASH Miami FL</a></p>
<p>Fall of 2012 will be an exciting time for the DASH store in Miami.  The Kardashians will be in town for the recording of their new reality TV show Kourtney and Kim Take Miami.  The show will premier on <a href="http://www.eonline.com/news/346316/new-season-of-kourtney-kim-take-miami-announced-we-ve-got-all-the-deets">E!</a> in January 2013.";s:10:"post_title";s:10:"DASH Miami";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:10:"dash-miami";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2012-09-25 15:22:50";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2012-09-25 22:22:50";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:11;s:4:"guid";s:48:"http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/?page_id=128";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:2:"20";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}}